description:
In this edition of To Trendow, To The Wall, Jack and Miles discuss Captain Kirk finally going to space, Katie Couric admitting to editing out negative comments in RBG interview, Jamie Costa's incredible Robin Williams impersonation, Herschel Walker cancelling fundraiser with supporter who had swastika in her Twitter profile, LaVar Ball's embarassingly ugly and expensive sneakers, and Pornhub's porn search map.
